            and <a href="https://uipotion.com/potions-index.json" target="_blank" rel="noopener">potions-index</a>),
            give it the schemas in <code>src/statics/schemas/</code> and existing potions in the same category as
            references, and ask it to draft a new potion (Markdown + JSON + index entry). Then run
            <code>npm run validate</code>, tweak if needed, and open a PR. Many contributors use AI for the first draft
